So I know the a SlewRateLimiter can be used for velocity control instead of a trapezoid profile.

But I’d like to use a Trapezoid profile instead, in fact I’d like to make my own version of a TrapezoidProfile just for the velocity.

Is it just as simple as take the TrapeProfile: position → velocity, velocity → acceleration, acceleration → jerk and Jerk is Double.PosInfinity (or neg Infinity)
